title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Fix broken landing challenges
description:
In this how to I will show you how you can troubleshoot issues with landing challenges which are not working anymore. In my case I was hitting the issue with the strong wind landing challenges in Gibraltar and Funchal (at least I thought they were only affected ;-)). The error I received was that content or at least an item of the content was missing.
In this video I will show you step by step how I approached the issue and eventually found the root cause.
